R Studio IDE shortcuts 
----------------------
Ctrl U         // delete before cursor
Ctrl K         // delete after cursor 
Ctrl Alt R     // make new section
Ctrl D         // delete line
Ctrl W         // close window
Alt -          // <- assignment operator
Ctrl Shift M   // %>% pipe
Ctr Alt T      // run section of code
tab            // suggestions, and tab again to accept

Ctrl 1         // move to source
Ctrl 2         // move to console

Ctrl L         // clear console

Ctrl Alt M     // commit git project